OOC: heres my profile for my other 2 Tripred characters


NAME: Crusher

AFFILIATION: Tripredacus

SUB-AFFILIATION: Triceratops

PRIMARY WEAPON: 

Beast mode: Head
            

Transformer: 1x Horn Punch
             1x Fusion Blast
             1x Sonic Charge
             1x Solar Flare


FUNCTION: Combat Officer / Warrior

AFFILIATION: 

Beastmode: A huge Triceratops that can smash a transformer into 
pieces when he head butts him with his 2 razor sharp horns

Transform mode: Stands at 16 feet yellowish orange color with his 
left hand as his Triceratops head its 2 top horns shot out made from 
liquid metal with a range of 50 feet that's able to go thought even 
the strongest metals




NAME: Spike

AFFILIATION: Tripredacus

SUB-AFFILIATION: Armadillo  

PRIMARY WEAPON: 

Beast mode: rock crusher
            Spike shell

Transformer: 1x Rock Cracker
             1x Spike Shell
	       1x laser eyes
             1x Spider Mines (small mines with 4 legs that hide 
                themselves in the ground and charge target when they 
                come to close
             1x Tri-Cannon (3 lasers mounted together in a triangle 
                that fire together or in rapid fire)

FUNCTION: Tactic officer / Warrior

AFFILIATION: 

Land Mode: his body transform into his body and turn into a purple 
sphere that can move at great speed and he can crush transformers 
armor with his spikes and weight

Siege Mode: his whole underbody hides under the ground leaving his 
shell above ground and his tri-cannon comes out of his body and fires 
powerful blast into the sky that fall down on its target at great 
distance
 
Beastmode: A large Armadillo with a purple shell that can take a atom 
bomb without much of a scratch when he's curled up in a ball

Tranform mode: stands same high as most transformers his armored back 
is formed into a oval shield on his right arm with his tri-cannon 
connected to the end so he doesn't have to hold it to fire or even 
drop it 



BIC: back at the Tripredacus base 2 statis pod stood hooked up to the 
wall both flashing bright white before they opened and 2 transformers 
stepped out "its about time he walk us up" the larger one said 
stretching his arms out
